headline.print_headline: China, South Korea 'Effectively' Conclude Free Trade Deal
headline.main: China, South Korea 'Effectively' Conclude Free Trade Deal

lead_paragraph: Chinese and South Korean leaders said on Monday the two countries have "effectively" concluded a free trade agreement that will remove or sharply reduce barriers to trade and investment between the two trading giants.
